race.comment: MUST SEE (3) beaten last start over the 275m at Cannington but finished in the minors in a fast 16.03. Hard to top on the time from last start. SWEETIE PIE (1) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing second behind Night Lighter (17.20) in a OPEN. Strong form has emerged from her last run. Bold showing expected. REDHOT MONEY (7) was a winner (16.87) at this track two back but out of the placings last time when 8th there. Form here at the trip excellent including four wins. The form out of her last race has been franked. Cannot be taken lightly. SON OF SPIKE (2) is always hard to beat when he races at this trip.
